dct_title_s: Frankreich 1:25 000 / herausgegeben vom OKH/ GenStdH, Chef des Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesens.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, contours and spot heights. Depth shown by isolines. Geographic coordinates are given in grades (Paris principal meridian) and degrees (Greenwich meridian). Grid: Franz. Lambert Zone II, Zentral. Some sheets overprinted with Franz. Lambert-Gitter. Some areTruppenausgabe edition. Includes sources of map. Some are: herausgegeben vom Oberkommando des Heeres Gen Std H. Abt f Kr Karte u Verm Wess (II). SheetNr. XIII-10/1-2-3  Vaast la Hougue 1-2-3  was printed on  a map of part of Scotland on verso [Scale is not given.] Stamp of AMS number is crossed out. German stamp number "German M 861" on map. Includes index to corresponding 1:80 000 sheets
dct_creator_sm: Germany. Heer. Abteilung für Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesen
dct_publisher_sm: [Berlin] : OKH/GenStdH Chef des Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesen, 1942-1944
